data.description: Welcome to 725 W Walnut, Drumright, OK – A Charming Farmhouse Retreat!   Nestled within the popular M Jones addition, this property offers a picturesque slice of country living with all the modern comforts.  This farmhouse boasts 3 Bedrooms, providing cozy sanctuaries for your family.  Enjoy 1 well-appointed Bathroom, beautifully designed for your convenience.  A 2-car Garage ensures your vehicles are protected from the elements.  With 1092 square feet of living space, this home offers the perfect balance of comfort and coziness.  Built in 1973, this farmhouse exudes timeless charm while seamlessly integrating modern updates.  Sitting on an expansive 7 lots, this property allows for endless possibilities and space to roam.  Inside, you'll find tasteful LVP flooring and planked ceilings, blending rustic charm with contemporary style.  Step outside to your oasis: a covered back patio, perfect for al fresco dining and relaxation.  The property is enclosed with perimeter fencing, ensuring privacy and security.  Modern upgrades include updated HVAC, electrical, and plumbing, providing peace of mind for years to come.  This property is more than a house; it's a story waiting to be written. Come home to the tranquility of Drumright and experience the charm of small-town living.  Contact us today to make this farmhouse your own!
